1. *Njemu* je bilo važno da se zabavi na zabavi. (It was important to him to have fun at the party.)
2. Ona je pokazala *njemu* ljubav na svaki mogući način. (She showed him love in every way possible.)
3. Ona mu je obećala da će uvek biti tu za *njega*. (She promised him she would always be there for him.)
4. On je učinio sve što je mogao da zadovolji *njegove* potrebe. (He did all he could to fulfill his needs.)
5. Ona je pružila *njemu* neizmernu podršku u teškim trenucima. (She gave him immeasurable support in hard times.)
6. On je uvek bio tu da pruži ruku pomoći *njemu*. (He was always there to lend a helping hand to him.)